snippet.title: Lovesick - Official Reveal Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Here's your look at Lovesick in this trailer for the upcoming puzzle escape room VR game. Join director/writer Corey Warning to learn about the story set up for Lovesick, your mission to explore escape room-styled areas, and the characters of the game. Lovesick will be available on Meta Quest and SteamVR in 2025.
